  <brief_title>Intraoperative Electrical Impedance Tomography in Obese Patients Undergoing Robotic Assisted Radical Prostatectomy.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Optimization of Intraoperative Ventilation Guided by Electrical Impedance Tomography in Combination With Oxygen Saturation by Pulse Oximetry (SpO2) Versus SpO2 Alone in Obese Patients Undergoing Robotic Assisted Radical Prostatectomy: Prospective Randomized Trial</official_title>
