  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of our study will be verify a possible improvement in arterial&#xD;
      oxygenation in the obese patient undergoing robotic-assisted radical prostatectomy if the&#xD;
      ventilation will be guided by electrical impedance tomography rather than peripheral&#xD;
      saturation alone.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
